If we run the math and calculate the reachability entropy for Society 1 using Shannon's logarithmic

31:28.520 --> 31:33.480
formula based on those distinct proportions, it comes out to roughly 0.918 bits.

31:33.920 --> 31:35.220
0.918 bits of entropy.

31:35.480 --> 31:35.800
Got it.

