Just 15 people fighting for the exact same political crown in the exact same arena.

31:59.260 --> 31:59.520
Wow.

31:59.820 --> 32:01.280
And the entropy for Society 3?

32:01.400 --> 32:02.300
Strictly zero bits.

32:02.720 --> 32:03.060
Zero.

32:03.440 --> 32:05.600
Because there is no diversity of future types.

32:05.680 --> 32:06.040
Exactly.

