Unity of action is indeed efficient, but unity of capability is fatal.

32:32.300 --> 32:33.420
Unity of capability.

32:33.500 --> 32:33.760
Yes.

32:33.760 --> 32:37.440
This is the core of the paper's theorem three, distinction collapse.

